0201
  -Define Class-
    Functions for Classes:
      get_declared_classes(); // Returns an array of declared classes
      class_exists($string);  // Returns T/F if the class(args) exists

0202
  -Instances/Objects-
      Functions for Instances:
        get_class($object): // Returns the name of object's class
        is_a($object, $string); // Returns T/F if the obj has the same class name as the string(2nd arg)

0203
  -Class Properties-
    Functions for Properties:
      get_class_vars($string); // Returns a assoc array of props that are defined in this class
      get_object_vars($object); // Returns the current vars/props of this instance/object
      property_exists($mixed(class/object), $string); // Returns T/F if the property(2nd arg) exists in the class/obj(1st arg)

0204
  -Class Methods-
    Functions for Methods:
      get_class_methods($mixed(class/object)); // Returns the different methods available on it
      method_exists($mixed, $string); // Returns T/F if the method(2nd arg) exists on the object/class(1st arg)

0205
  -Class Methods-
  -Refer to an Instance-
    Outside the class: $variable->
    Inside the class: $this->

0206
  -Challenge 01-

0301
  -Class Inheritance-

0302
  -Class Inheritance-
  -Define a Subclass-
    functions for Inheritance:
      get_parent_class($mixed); // Takes class/instance as an argument and returns the name of the parent class
      is_subclass_of($mixed, $string); // Takes class/instance as an argument(1st arg) and checks if subclass of parent(2nd arg)
      class_parents($mixed); // Returns all parent classes of class/instance

